<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <%- include("../shared/head", { pageTitle: "Orbit | Home" }) %>
  <body class="page-home">
    <%- include("../shared/header") %>
    <main class="container hero hero-landing">
      <div class="hero-mission-frame">
        <div class="hero-console-bar">
          <span class="hero-console-bar__program">Orbit · flight ops</span>
          <span class="hero-console-bar__met">
            <abbr title="Your device local time">LCL</abbr>
            <span
              class="hero-console-bar__nums hero-console-bar__clock"
              id="hero-console-local-time"
              aria-live="polite"
              aria-atomic="true"
            >00:00:00</span>
          </span>
          <span class="hero-console-bar__mode">Traj · att · timeline</span>
          <span class="hero-console-bar__filler"></span>
          <span class="hero-console-bar__badge">ops ready</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-landing-inner">
        <section class="hero-card hero-card--landing">
          <p class="badge">Mission-style console</p>
          <h1>Flight-ops dashboard style—trajectory, attitude, and MET in one glance.</h1>
          <ul class="hero-skim" role="list">
            <li>
              <span class="hero-skim-label">Trajectory</span>
              <span class="hero-skim-text">Raw logs → live ground track &amp; orbit on the globe. No hand-built ETL.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="hero-skim-label">Attitude</span>
              <span class="hero-skim-text">3D vehicle orientation in a side panel next to the map—quick to read under load.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="hero-skim-label">MET &amp; events</span>
              <span class="hero-skim-text">Mission clock, phases, and callouts aligned with what’s on screen.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="hero-actions hero-actions--landing">
            <% if (!isAuth) { %>
              <a href="/signup" class="button button-primary">Get started</a>
              <a href="/login" class="button button-secondary button-secondary--light">Log in</a>
            <% } else { %>
              <a href="/tracker" class="button button-primary">Open tracker</a>
            <% } %>
          </div>
        </section>
        <aside class="hero-landing-aside">
          <figure class="hero-orbit-panel">
            <figcaption class="hero-orbit-title">Chat · trajectory review</figcaption>
            <div class="hero-orbit-svg-wrap hero-collab-wrap">
              <div
                class="hero-collab-chat"
                role="group"
                aria-label="Illustrative flight-ops chat: plotting altitude, correcting fusion, adding MET markers."
              >
                <div class="hero-collab-bubble hero-collab-bubble--user hero-collab-bubble--s1">
                  <span class="hero-collab-bubble__meta">You</span>
                  <p class="hero-collab-bubble__text">
                    Plot rocket altitude vs. MET from this TeleMega log—trajectory only, English labels.
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-collab-bubble hero-collab-bubble--ai hero-collab-bubble--s2">
                  <span class="hero-collab-bubble__meta">Model</span>
                  <p class="hero-collab-bubble__text">
                    First pass plotted. Boost is noisy on baro; coast looks plausible. Say the word if you want sensor fusion.
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-collab-bubble hero-collab-bubble--user hero-collab-bubble--s3">
                  <span class="hero-collab-bubble__meta">You</span>
                  <p class="hero-collab-bubble__text">
                    Hold on—that dip right after apogee doesn’t match GPS. Re-blend baro with GPS, tighten the EKF innovation gate, and redraw the profile.
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-collab-bubble hero-collab-bubble--ai hero-collab-bubble--s4">
                  <span class="hero-collab-bubble__meta">Model</span>
                  <p class="hero-collab-bubble__text">
                    Regenerated with GPS/baro fusion and a stricter gate—the spurious notch is gone; coast tracks your ground truth better.
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-collab-bubble hero-collab-bubble--user hero-collab-bubble--s5">
                  <span class="hero-collab-bubble__meta">You</span>
                  <p class="hero-collab-bubble__text">
                    Nice. Add vertical MET markers for staging burn-out and apogee so it matches the tracker timeline.
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-collab-bubble hero-collab-bubble--ai hero-collab-bubble--s6">
                  <span class="hero-collab-bubble__meta">Model</span>
                  <p class="hero-collab-bubble__text">
                    Markers pinned at your event table—T+ synced to the same mission clock as the globe view.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <svg
                class="hero-orbit-svg hero-collab-svg"
                viewBox="0 0 320 220"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                role="img"
                aria-label="Monochrome animation: operator and AI discuss flight data; draft altitude profile is corrected and annotated with MET markers."
              >
                <defs>
                  <linearGradient id="heroCollabGrad" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
                    <stop offset="0%" stop-color="rgba(255,255,255,0)" />
                    <stop offset="45%" stop-color="rgba(255,255,255,0.14)" />
                    <stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(255,255,255,0)" />
                  </linearGradient>
                </defs>
                <g opacity="0.35" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.3)" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
                  <line x1="20" y1="48" x2="300" y2="48" stroke-width="0.5" />
                  <line x1="20" y1="86" x2="300" y2="86" stroke-width="0.5" />
                  <line x1="20" y1="124" x2="300" y2="124" stroke-width="0.5" />
                  <line x1="20" y1="162" x2="300" y2="162" stroke-width="0.5" />
                  <line x1="56" y1="28" x2="56" y2="178" stroke-width="0.5" />
                  <line x1="124" y1="28" x2="124" y2="178" stroke-width="0.5" />
                  <line x1="192" y1="28" x2="192" y2="178" stroke-width="0.5" />
                  <line x1="260" y1="28" x2="260" y2="178" stroke-width="0.5" />
                </g>
                <rect
                  x="40"
                  y="36"
                  width="240"
                  height="148"
                  rx="3"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.14)"
                  stroke-width="1"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                />
                <text
                  class="hero-collab-label"
                  x="48"
                  y="50"
                  fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.4)"
                  font-size="9"
                  font-family="ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace"
                  letter-spacing="0.12em"
                >
                  ALT (m) · VS MET
                </text>
                <!-- Draft profile: spurious dip after apogee (baro artifact) -->
                <path
                  class="hero-collab-draft"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.72)"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  pathLength="100"
                  stroke-dasharray="100"
                  stroke-dashoffset="100"
                  d="M 44 162 C 82 162, 98 128, 124 92 C 148 64, 172 70, 182 88 C 192 118, 198 108, 212 98 C 228 86, 248 118, 276 150"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                />
                <!-- Fused / corrected profile -->
                <path
                  class="hero-collab-refined"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.95)"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  pathLength="100"
                  stroke-dasharray="100"
                  stroke-dashoffset="100"
                  d="M 44 162 C 88 162, 104 124, 132 90 C 156 62, 188 66, 212 92 C 232 112, 252 132, 276 150"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                />
                <g class="hero-collab-markers" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.45)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3 4" aria-hidden="true">
                  <line class="hero-collab-marker hero-collab-marker--a" x1="118" y1="42" x2="118" y2="168" />
                  <line class="hero-collab-marker hero-collab-marker--b" x1="168" y1="42" x2="168" y2="168" />
                </g>
                <text
                  class="hero-collab-marker-label hero-collab-marker-label--a"
                  x="118"
                  y="186"
                  text-anchor="middle"
                  fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.38)"
                  font-size="7.5"
                  font-family="ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace"
                  letter-spacing="0.08em"
                >
                  STAGING
                </text>
                <text
                  class="hero-collab-marker-label hero-collab-marker-label--b"
                  x="168"
                  y="186"
                  text-anchor="middle"
                  fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.38)"
                  font-size="7.5"
                  font-family="ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace"
                  letter-spacing="0.08em"
                >
                  APOGEE
                </text>
                <rect
                  x="92"
                  y="198"
                  width="136"
                  height="14"
                  fill="url(#heroCollabGrad)"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-orbit-blocks">
              <div class="hero-orbit-block">
                <h3 class="hero-orbit-block-title">Data ingest</h3>
                <p class="hero-orbit-block-tag">Raw → live orbit</p>
                <p class="hero-orbit-block-text">Drop telemetry or logs; the globe updates the track for you.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="hero-orbit-block">
                <h3 class="hero-orbit-block-title">Attitude</h3>
                <p class="hero-orbit-block-tag">3D · beside map</p>
                <p class="hero-orbit-block-text">Rocket pose where operators expect it—next to the trajectory view.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="hero-orbit-block">
                <h3 class="hero-orbit-block-title">Mission clock</h3>
                <p class="hero-orbit-block-tag">T+ · phases</p>
                <p class="hero-orbit-block-text">Elapsed time and milestones tied to the same display state.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </figure>
        </aside>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <script>
      (function () {
        var el = document.getElementById("hero-console-local-time");
        if (!el) return;
        function pad(n) {
          return String(n).padStart(2, "0");
        }
        function tick() {
          var d = new Date();
          el.textContent = pad(d.getHours()) + ":" + pad(d.getMinutes()) + ":" + pad(d.getSeconds());
        }
        tick();
        setInterval(tick, 1000);
      })();
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
